config RTL8196E_ETH
	tristate "Realtek RTL8196E Ethernet (new, recommended)"
	depends on MIPS && OF
	depends on !RTL819X
	help
	  Clean-room RTL8196E Ethernet driver: single-port, NAPI, zero-copy
	  RX/TX. Replaces the legacy rtl819x SDK port with maintainable code.

	  Delivers ~91 Mbps TCP RX and ~44 Mbps TCP TX on the Lexra RLX4181
	  (RTL8196E at 400 MHz). Configured via devicetree (interface@0 node).
